title: Piz Terza
text:
Piz Terza (also known as "Urtirolaspitz") is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in the <a href="Sesvenna%20Range">Sesvenna Range</a> of the <a href="Alps">Alps</a>, located on the border between <a href="Italy">Italy</a> and <a href="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>.
The closest locality is <a href="M%C3%BCstair">Müstair</a>.
